snippet.title: Open Mod [DEFUSAL GAME MODE TEASER]
snippet.description:
Hi, we're back with a new short teaser featuring Demolition/Defusal game mode. More videos to come! Stay tuned!
Scroll for more ↓

We've got a brand new website : https://open-mod.com/
Support us on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/OpenMod
Add to your wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1591680/Open_Mod/

We also have the Kickstarter pre-launch page live but we might not launch it because of the tax rates. We'd like to go with the Patreon way but you can subscribe to the Kickstarter page anyway, link here: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/hypergamey/open-mod-project

More:
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/mPMYwkpKPj
Twitter: https://twitter.com/OpenModNews
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/hypergamey.studio/
Email: contact@hypergamey.studio

#unity3d  #indiedev #freetoplay #fps #showcase

Soundtrack: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eQT2tgpjwcU&ab_channel=Fuzzeke
